{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Nonlinear Curve Fitting with L-BFGS\n\nFit nonlinear parametric models to noisy data using `np_minimize`. The **symbolic-numeric bridge** is central: we define the model symbolically, derive the sum-of-squares gradient with `diff()`, then implement it numerically — a workflow impossible in pure numeric environments.\n\n1. **Exponential decay** $y = A e^{-kt} + c$ [S+N]\n2. **Gaussian peak** $y = A \\exp\\!\\left(-\\frac{(x-\\mu)^2}{2\\sigma^2}\\right)$ [S+N]\n3. **Linearized vs nonlinear comparison**\n4. **Confidence intervals** via the Jacobian",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"numerics-optimize\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 1,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 1. Exponential Decay: $y = A e^{-kt} + c$ [S+N]\n\n### Symbolic Phase: Deriving the Gradient\n\nThe per-point squared-error loss is\n$$L_i(A, k, c) = \\tfrac{1}{2}\\bigl(y_i - A e^{-k t_i} - c\\bigr)^2$$\n\nWe use `diff()` to derive partial derivatives with respect to each parameter.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Per-point model and loss */\nmodel_i(A, k, c, t_i) := A * exp(-k * t_i) + c$\nL_i(A, k, c, t_i, y_i) := (1/2) * (y_i - model_i(A, k, c, t_i))^2$\n\n/* Symbolic partial derivatives */\ndL_dA : diff(L_i(A, k, c, t[i], y[i]), A);\ndL_dk : diff(L_i(A, k, c, t[i], y[i]), k);\ndL_dc : diff(L_i(A, k, c, t[i], y[i]), c);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 2,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "-(%e^-(t[i]*k)*(y[i]-c-%e^-(t[i]*k)*A))\n%e^-(t[i]*k)*A*t[i]*(y[i]-c-%e^-(t[i]*k)*A)"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "-y_{i}+c+e^ {- \\left(t_{i}\\,k\\right) }\\,A"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 2,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "The residual $r_i = A e^{-k t_i} + c - y_i$ appears in all three:\n- $\\frac{\\partial L_i}{\\partial A} = r_i \\cdot e^{-k t_i}$\n- $\\frac{\\partial L_i}{\\partial k} = -r_i \\cdot A\\, t_i\\, e^{-k t_i}$\n- $\\frac{\\partial L_i}{\\partial c} = r_i$\n\nSumming over all data points gives the full gradient.\n\n### Numeric Phase: Generate Data and Optimize",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* True parameters: A=5, k=0.3, c=1 */\nn : 50$\nt_data : np_linspace(0, 10, n)$\nnoise : np_scale(0.3, np_randn([n]))$\ny_data : np_add(\n  np_add(np_scale(5.0, np_exp(np_scale(-0.3, t_data))), 1.0),\n  noise)$\nprint(\"Generated\", n, \"noisy observations\")$\nprint(\"True: A=5, k=0.3, c=1\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 3,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Generated 50 noisy observations\nTrue: A=5, k=0.3, c=1"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Cost and gradient — implementing the symbolic derivatives above */\nexp_cost(params) := block([A_val, k_val, c_val, pred, res],\n  A_val : np_ref(params, 0),\n  k_val : np_ref(params, 1),\n  c_val : np_ref(params, 2),\n  pred : np_add(np_scale(A_val, np_exp(np_scale(-k_val, t_data))), c_val),\n  res : np_sub(pred, y_data),\n  np_sum(np_pow(res, 2)) / (2 * n))$\n\nexp_grad(params) := block([A_val, k_val, c_val, e_kt, pred, res],\n  A_val : np_ref(params, 0),\n  k_val : np_ref(params, 1),\n  c_val : np_ref(params, 2),\n  e_kt : np_exp(np_scale(-k_val, t_data)),\n  pred : np_add(np_scale(A_val, e_kt), c_val),\n  res : np_sub(pred, y_data),\n  /* Gradient from symbolic derivation */\n  ndarray([\n    np_sum(np_mul(res, e_kt)) / n,\n    -np_sum(np_mul(np_mul(res, np_scale(A_val, t_data)), e_kt)) / n,\n    np_sum(res) / n\n  ]))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 4,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Initial guess (deliberately off) */\np0 : ndarray([1.0, 1.0, 0.0])$\n[p_opt, loss_opt, converged] : np_minimize(exp_cost, exp_grad, p0)$\n\nA_fit : np_ref(p_opt, 0)$\nk_fit : np_ref(p_opt, 1)$\nc_fit : np_ref(p_opt, 2)$\nprint(\"Fitted: A =\", A_fit, \", k =\", k_fit, \", c =\", c_fit)$\nprint(\"True:   A = 5, k = 0.3, c = 1\")$\nprint(\"Loss:\", loss_opt, \" Converged:\", converged)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 5,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "*************************************************\n  N=    3   NUMBER OF CORRECTIONS= 3\n       INITIAL VALUES\n F=  3.723107552983336D+00   GNORM=  2.531628224447235D+00\n*************************************************\n   I  NFN     FUNC                    GNORM                   STEPLENGTH\n   1    2     1.687071541559957D+00   1.549320579649373D+00   3.950027062991620D-01\n  26   32     6.338349441517671D-02   4.299280944043438D-11   1.000000000000000D+00\n THE MINIMIZATION TERMINATED WITHOUT DETECTING ERRORS.\n IFLAG = 0\nFitted: A = 4.953573796500634 , k = 0.31166915597636485 , c =\n           1.0286091924468495\nTrue:   A = 5, k = 0.3, c = 1\nLoss: 0.06338349441517671  Converged: true"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "ax_draw2d(\n  color=\"red\", marker_size=5, name=\"Noisy data\",\n  points(np_to_list(t_data), np_to_list(y_data)),\n  color=\"blue\", line_width=2, name=\"Fitted: A*exp(-k*t)+c\",\n  explicit(A_fit * exp(-k_fit * t) + c_fit, t, 0, 10),\n  color=\"gray\", dash=\"dash\", name=\"True curve\",\n  explicit(5 * exp(-0.3*t) + 1, t, 0, 10),\n  title=\"Exponential Decay Fit\", xlabel=\"t\", ylabel=\"y\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 6,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
